column5: Once you enter through the main doors at Hall 5, the "will call" desk is usually on the right hand side of the lobby.  Identify yourself as an OFC winner as there will be a separate envelope set aside for your tickets. There will be a "Will Call" sign directly above the area.  Below is the list of winners that I have... if your not on this list I don't have you down.. I went through all my pms to look for winners..
